  "description": {
    "zh": "雇佣兵，还有另一个任务要交给你。我们的人需要了解某些武器的性能，他们提到了托卡列夫步枪。\n我们认为你已经足够熟练完成这样的任务，所以选择了你。\n\n你需要用托卡列夫步枪再次清除 PMC 和 Rogue。别让我们失望，雇佣兵，我们相信这对你来说不成问题。",
    "en": "Another job for you merc. Our men need to know about the performance of certain weapons, they were talking about Tokarev rifles.\nWe think you are already skilled enough for such a task, which is why we chose you for this.\n\nYou need to get rid of operators and the USEC rogues again, while using Tokarev rifles. Don't disappoint us mercenary, we don't think this will be a problem for you."
  },
